  "data": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>When you attempt a check for a skill associated with an Athletics sphere package you possess, your armor check penalty on that check for wearing armor you are proficient in is reduced by 2. For every 4 ranks in the skill associated with the package you possess, the penalty is further reduced by 1 (this cannot reduce your armor check penalty below 0). The benefits granted by this talent do not stack with those provided by the Armored Athlete feat. <strong>Associated Feat:</strong> Armored Athlete.</p>\n",
